WEBVTT


00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.760
Issues addressed here,

00:00:01.761 --> 00:00:05.841
I think make space for the youth to be involved in things.

00:00:05.842 --> 00:00:07.841
Have these, like this panel discussion,

00:00:07.842 --> 00:00:10.441
for example. Make the youth involving decision making process.

